<item>
            <title>[TIKA-34] Provide a method that will return a default configuration (TikaConfig).</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-34</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Although a default configuration is available, one must explicitly specify its location and open a stream from that location.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be helpful to have a method that returns the default configuration, parsed and ready to use, so that the users can be insulated from the implementation of how and where we store it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
